about.summary: Simulated Annealing (simulated annealing optimization) in Python

name: simanneal
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "simanneal" %}
{% set version = "0.4.2" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 0657354bacd503ff5fc0b984110be7b174ecedbb976caf1c230c73a128a06d5a

build:
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed --no-cache-dir -vvv "
  noarch: python

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - simanneal

about:
  home: https://github.com/perrygeo/simanneal
  license: ISC
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: '{{ environ["RECIPE_DIR"] }}/LICENSE.txt'
  summary: Simulated Annealing (simulated annealing optimization) in Python
  doc_url: https://github.com/perrygeo/simanneal
  dev_url: https://github.com/perrygeo/simanneal

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - tarcisiofischer
    - williamjamir
